"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-paralympics-paralympics-tickets-paris-2024-venues-games-b2603090.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Organisers believe that Paris 2024 may be the first Paralympic Games to sell out  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999986585, \"rank\": 1.3355641740284004e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Paris 2024has sold just over two million tickets for theParalympics, organisers said hours beforethe opening ceremonyon Wednesday, adding they were confident it would be a sold-out extravaganza.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 622, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Over two million tickets have already been sold for the Paris 2024 Paralympic Games, including one million in just one month,\\\" Paris 2024 said in a statement.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 681, \"end\": 691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999986585, \"rank\": 1.3355641740284004e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 692, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9976623324716759, \"rank\": 0.0016065163209548754, \"text\": \"Paralympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers said on Tuesday that some500,000 tickets were still up for grabs, which, if they are sold, would put Paris just short of the record 2.7 million sold for the London 2012 Games, where 97% tickets were purchased.\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 1005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.13558704408636e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Beijing 2008 Games, 1.82 million tickets were sold and organisers distributed 1.62 million to schools, according to International Paralympic Committee (IPC) figures.\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee (IPC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee (IPC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 2.1 million tickets were sold for the Rio 2016 Paralympics.\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9263632640790865, \"rank\": 0.0794899506032975, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024, however, is confident the Paralympics will be sold out, which would be a first.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999986585, \"rank\": 1.3355641740284004e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know we will continue to sell tickets over the next days, probably until the end of the Games,\\\" Paris 2024 president Tony Estanguet said.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999986585, \"rank\": 1.3355641740284004e-11, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Estanguet\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Estanguet\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was the case at the Olympics, we sold tickets until the very last day, even the last hour, and that's been very exciting for us to see that fans were excited until the end and really wanted to take the last opportunities.\\\"\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\"